thread.title: Greg Le Lacheur
thread.title_full: Servcorp reviewed by Greg Le Lacheur

author: Greg Le Lacheur
title: Greg Le Lacheur
text:
I have been at Servcorp Chifley Tower for nearly 6 six years continuously.I have found the services of the team to be of a very high standard and would recommend Chifley offices to anyone.Having the flexibility to utilise the teams services on a needs only basis is very helpful to cashflow and business planning especially with a growing business.The team are an important part of my business and I look forward to walking through the door each morning to this pleasant and elegant office.
Gregory Le Lacheur
